The paper deals with the design and typing of distributed XML documents, which involves issues related to data management, distributed computing, and software engineering. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.PL (Programming Languages), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
